  "texts": [
    "To assess the broader applicability of our framesemantics-based fact-checking system, we conducted a comprehensive coverage analysis.",
    "For this analysis, we used the frames discussed in Arslan et al. (2020), including the 11 newly defined frames from their work.",
    "Because the annotations available for the fact-checking frames are limited, we employed a zero-shot GPT-4o-mini model (detailed in Appendix E.1) to identify frames evoked in the PolitiFact fact-check corpus.",
    "Claims that did not trigger any of our studied frames were classified as \"None.\"",
    "The distribution of frames is presented in Table 2."
